---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - Fairly Odd Streamers"
  description="Learn about Fairly Odd Streamers, a resource hub for livestreamers."
>

<div class="section-narrow">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h1 style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">About Fairly Odd Streamers</h1>

      <p>
        Fairly Odd Streamers is a curated resource hub dedicated to helping livestreamers succeed. We believe that
        content creators deserve access to the best tools, sponsorship opportunities, and insights to build thriving
        streaming communities.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        To empower livestreamers with curated resources, sponsorship opportunities, and actionable insights. We focus on
        quality over quantity, ensuring every recommendation has been vetted and tested.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">What We Offer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>100+ verified sponsorship and affiliate opportunities</li>
        <li>Analytics tools to measure and improve your streams</li>
        <li>Chat bots and moderation solutions</li>
        <li>Graphics, overlays, and design resources</li>
        <li>Free music and sound libraries</li>
        <li>Professional broadcasting software recommendations</li>
        <li>Expert interviews with top streamers</li>
        <li>Actionable guides and tips</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        Fairly Odd Streamers is a project by streaming enthusiasts who understand the challenges content creators face.
        We've tested these tools and sponsorships ourselves and are committed to maintaining high standards.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Have a tool or sponsorship opportunity you'd like us to feature? Found an error? We'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
